label: A5B2_oP14_59_a2e_e-001
title: Shcherbinaite (V$_{2}$O$_{5}$) Structure ({\em Revised})
comments: An earlier version of this structure found by (Ketelaar, 1936) \href{current_web_home_dir/A5B2_oP14_31_a2b_b-001}{was given the $D8_{7}$} {\em Strukturbericht} designation in (Gottfried, 1938). It was later realized that this structure had a rather unexpected arrangement of vanadium atoms, and the structure was revised by (Enjalbert, 1986) and others.
